      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3 in pristine condition. This specimen is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing for a razor-sharp throttle response. The power is delivered through a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis is structurally flawless, with documented subframe reinforcement and rod bearing service already completed. Every bushing is tight, and the suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications, ensuring peak lateral acceleration and communicative feedback. This is a mechanically superlative example with impeccable paint depth and zero signs of thermal cycling wear.",
