      "description": "Offered here is a truly exceptional vehicle that presents in showroom condition, appearing as if it just rolled off the assembly line. The exterior paint is flawless, boasting a deep, glass-like luster without a single swirl mark, rock chip, or blemish, thanks to a lifetime of climate-controlled garage storage and professional ceramic coating. Every body panel is original with perfect alignment. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the leather remains supple with no bolster wear, the carpets are spotless, and the interior still carries a faint new-car scent. All electronics, switches, and displays function perfectly. Mechanically, this car is peerless. It has been maintained with an open-wallet philosophy, with every service performed exclusively by master technicians using OEM parts. The engine bay is immaculate, and the undercarriage is as clean as the top side. This is a rare opportunity for a meticulous buyer to own a flagship example with a comprehensive service history and zero excuses.",
